# Selenium Server

description 'Selenium {{ sel_role.upper() }} Service'

start on filesystem or runlevel [2345]
stop on runlevel [!2345]

### Keep the process alive, limit to 5 restarts in 60s

  respawn
  respawn limit 5 60

### Start Selenium Server

  exec sudo -u {{ sel_user }} java -jar {{ sel_home }}/{{ sel_jar }} {{ sel_opts }}
